*Natalia Yurchenko (born 1965), gymnast
*Ivan V. Zaitsev (born 1975), Russian-born Kazakhstani water polo player

==Twin cities==

Norilsk is twinned with two other cities:

* Minusinsk, Krasnoyarsk Territory
* Nesebar, Bulgaria

